timelineItems.name: Hudson River Blue
timelineItems.text: Villa tries to uncork a bit of magic there, but the ball wants nowt to do with that. Deric saves. #NYCFC

timelineItems.name: Heather Yeo MD
timelineItems.text: Love that #NYCFC is trending on Twitter! It's about time. @ThirdRailSC @NYCFC let win this!

timelineItems.name: Teshawn Edmonds
timelineItems.text: Attendance at @Yankees Stadium: 26,211 (per @Christian_Araos) #NYCvHOU

timelineItems.name: Sixth Borough Blues
timelineItems.text: 86. Into the last 5 minutes at Yankee Stadium. Can NYCFC find the goal they so desperately need? #NYCFC #NYCvHOU

timelineItems.name: Jeffrey C. Hawkins
timelineItems.text: 20,000 screaming New Yorkers. It's like the weekend platform at 57th and 7th -only fun. Let's go #NYCFC !
